= redcloth_template

== Description

This plugin registers a template handler for <tt>*.red</tt> files, which will
be run through ERB and RedCloth, and enables you to use Textile syntax directly
in your views.

Note: this plugin requires Rails 2.2 and at least RedCloth 4.0 (aka
"SuperRedCloth").

